name: もこもこしっぽ
description: ウサギの季節がやってきた！みんなで仲良く素敵なウサギの衣装に身を包み、草むらを駆け回る。そしてタマゴには色が塗られ、笑顔があふれる。ホリデーをぴょんぴょん楽しめますように！

skins.name: もこもこしっぽティーモ

wikiSkinData.lore: Eggs are lame, right? They're round. They break easily. Eggs need a major facelift. Introducing… Teemo! He's cute. He's annoying. But most of all, he'll paint all your eggs for you, maybe turning one or two (or seven) into life-threatening explosives.

skins.name: もこもこしっぽフィズ

wikiSkinData.lore: Rising from the fluffiest depths to crush all root vegetable cohorts, Fizz commands the greatest threat carrots have ever known—a killer rabbit with the foulest and cruelest of tempers.
